📚 Book Explorer — React Router & Props Project

🧠 Overview
**Book Explorer** is a simple and interactive web app built with **React, Vite, and React Router**.  
It allows users to explore a list of books, view detailed information, and learn basic React concepts like **props**, **routing**, and **hooks** (`useState`, `useEffect`, `useParams`).

⚙️ Features
✅ Displays a list of books  
✅ View detailed info (title, author, description, rating)  
✅ Dynamic routing using `react-router-dom`  
✅ Props-based data sharing between components  
✅ Simulated API data using `useEffect`  

